<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registro</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #FF85A2;
            --secondary-color: #FFC2D1;
            --accent-color: #7B2CBF;
            --background-color: #FFF0F3;
            --text-color: #2D3436;
        }
        body {
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .login-container {
            display: flex;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 800px;
        }
        .login-form {
            padding: 30px;
            width: 50%;
        }
        .login-banner {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .login-banner img {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            text-align: left;
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        input:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 133, 162, 0.5);
        }
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }
        a {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .login-banner a {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .login-banner a:hover {
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-form">
            <h1>Registro</h1>
            <form action="/auth/register" method="POST">
                <label for="username">Usuario:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
                <label for="password">Contraseña:</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
                <button type="submit">Registrarse</button>
            </form>
            <p>¿Ya tienes una cuenta? <a href="/">Inicia sesión aquí</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="login-banner">
            <img src="/uploads/logo.png" alt="Logo de Pastelería CRUD">
            <h2>Únete a Pastelería CRUD</h2>
            <p>Empieza a gestionar tus pasteles hoy mismo.</p>
            <a href="/">Iniciar Sesión</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
